Sumukha in <a href="/web/20220907100016/https://www.wisdomlib.org/sanskrit" title="Sanskrit glossary homepage"><span itemprop="name">Sanskrit glossary</span></a>
</small>
</div>
<!-- <div class="col-12 col-md-auto">
